name: Irene P. Tello, Ikebana Ink Series 01, 2021
description:
Collector of NFT receives a pack including .JPG Still Image + .mp4 Movement video + Tote Bag + T-shirt + Archival Giclee print edition. Size can be selected for the physical print, and postage details can be discussed via info@skyfinefoods.com. ****************************** Irene P Tello is a multi-disciplinary creative who works between the boundaries of Art & Design: Digital Media Art, Visual Design, Photography and Video (Still Image or Moving Image/Video)  Her work is mainly focused on digital escapism through organic — sensorial aesthetics as H20 and superfluid ecosystems.********   "The use of natural elements and their displacement in these immersive digital environments that have such a realistic organic appearance and vivid textures that invokes a new colourful paradigm"
